Name: libqt6xdg
Version: 4.0.1
Release: alt1

Summary: Qt implementation of freedesktop.org xdg specs
License: LGPL-2.1
Group: System/Libraries

Url: https://github.com/lxqt/libqtxdg
Source: %name-%version.tar

BuildRequires(pre): rpm-macros-qt6
